<para>Commits pass-level events. </para>
          </briefdescription>
          <detaileddescription>
<para>Events pushed via `UpdateContext::pushPass()` become readable in subsequent passes through `UpdateContext::readPass()`. <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1gameloop_1_1Pass" kindref="compound">Pass</ref> events are discarded at the end of the phase. </para>
